## SECTION 2 -- GRANT OF PATENT LICENSE

Subject to the terms and conditions of this License, each Licensor hereby grants to You a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive, perpetual, irrevocable license under any patent claims licensable by the Licensor that are necessarily infringed by the Licensed File as Conveyed by the Licensor, to make, have made, use, offer to sell, sell, import, and otherwise transfer Licensed Files and Covered Derivative Works.

**2.1 Patent License Termination.** Your patent license under this Section terminates automatically, and without further notice, if You institute, maintain, or threaten patent infringement litigation against any Licensor or any downstream recipient, alleging that any Licensed File or Derivative Work thereof infringes one or more patents held by You. Such termination:

> **(a)** affects only You and does not affect the patent licenses of other Licensees;
> **(b)** does not affect Your right to Propagate Licensed Files for personal use; and
> **(c)** does not affect the patent licenses of third parties who received Licensed Files before termination.

