**8.2 No Further Restrictions.** You may not place this License in combination with any other legal instrument or impose any contractual or technological measure that restricts downstream recipients in the exercise of rights expressly granted herein. You may not impose patent license obligations, copyleft encumbrances upon Independent Modules, or conditions of warranty, indemnification, or support as a prerequisite for receipt of Licensed Files.

**8.3 Dependency License Compliance.** This License does not govern the terms applicable to software dependencies used by Licensed Files. You must satisfy the license obligations of each dependency independently. No dependency's license terms encumber Licensed Files, and this License imposes no obligation upon dependencies.

